采取新的做法，但内塔尼亚胡仍坚持旧的幻想</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/post-war-gaza-warrants-a-fresh-approach-but-netanyahu-is-holding-on-to-old-fantasies/0000018d-1eeb-dd75-addd-feeb65050000</link><description>七十多年来，以色列提出了各种治理加沙的想法——从当地部族统治到将居民驱逐到西奈半岛。但巴勒斯坦人的变化需要新的方法</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 00:10:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/post-war-gaza-warrants-a-fresh-approach-but-netanyahu-is-holding-on-to-old-fantasies/0000018d-1eeb-dd75-addd-feeb65050000</guid></item><item><title>百万加沙人挤在南部：卫星图像显示巨大的新帐篷城</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-million-people-satellite-images-reveal-massive-tent-city-in-southern-gaza/0000018d-1cce-d022-ad9d-1efee5760000</link><description>过去几天拍摄的照片显示，拉法周围的空旷地区、人行道上和建筑物之间都出现了帐篷。 UNWRA 负责人表示，每个避难所可容纳约 20 人</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 23:41:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-million-people-satellite-images-reveal-massive-tent-city-in-southern-gaza/0000018d-1cce-d022-ad9d-1efee5760000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人不会喜欢玛莎·格森关于加沙战争的言论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israelis-wont-like-what-masha-gessen-has-to-say-about-the-gaza-war/0000018d-1d6d-d022-ad9d-1f7d5a360000</link><description>玛莎·格森 (Masha Gessen) 在苏联长大，以色列的存在是她的救生圈。现在，美国一位顶尖知识分子对国家提出了一些严厉的批评</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 23:30:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israelis-wont-like-what-masha-gessen-has-to-say-about-the-gaza-war/0000018d-1d6d-d022-ad9d-1f7d5a360000</guid></item><item><title>以色列画廊对艺术界对加沙战争的黑白反应作出反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/an-israeli-gallery-reacts-to-the-art-worlds-black-and-white-response-to-the-gaza-war/0000018d-1d80-db77-ad9f-dfb248ed0000</link><description>特拉维夫的纳西玛·兰道艺术基金会以其对国际当代艺术的关注而闻名。但目前那里的展览“光的光谱”仅展示以色列艺术家，所得收益将用于帮助重建被哈马斯摧毁的贝埃里基布兹美术馆</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 21:52:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/an-israeli-gallery-reacts-to-the-art-worlds-black-and-white-response-to-the-gaza-war/0000018d-1d80-db77-ad9f-dfb248ed0000</guid></item><item><title>抗议者在特拉维夫游行，要求加沙停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-18/ty-article/.premium/protesters-march-through-tel-aviv-to-demand-cease-fire-in-gaza/0000018d-1de9-dd75-addd-ffe932740000</link><description>数千人参加了最初被警方取消的抗议活动。 “站在一起”组织的赫利·米沙尔 (Heli Mishael) 对人群说：“经过 100 天的战争，人质还没有返回，无辜的巴勒斯坦人被杀害，我们仍然没有安全……还有另一种方法”</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 20:20:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-18/ty-article/.premium/protesters-march-through-tel-aviv-to-demand-cease-fire-in-gaza/0000018d-1de9-dd75-addd-ffe932740000</guid></item><item><title>人质家庭论坛和游戏社区在特拉维夫联手</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-18/ty-article/.premium/hostage-families-forum-and-gaming-community-join-forces-in-tel-aviv/0000018d-1ddf-dd75-addd-ffff1c190000</link><description>周五将在特拉维夫举行的黑客马拉松将鼓励以色列游戏行业的人们开发游戏，以提高人们对仍被关押在加沙的 136 名人质的认识</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 20:05:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-18/ty-article/.premium/hostage-families-forum-and-gaming-community-join-forces-in-tel-aviv/0000018d-1ddf-dd75-addd-ffff1c190000</guid></item><item><title>内阁官员：加沙战争没有未来 内塔尼亚胡正在消磨时间逃避责任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-18/ty-article/.premium/cabinet-official-the-war-has-no-future-netanyahu-is-killing-time-to-evade-responsibility/0000018d-1ddc-db77-ad9f-dffe7d5a0000</link><description>在 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击之前的几年里，内塔尼亚胡总理一直对审讯者说，“我不负责”。现在，他不仅试图消除对大屠杀的指责，还试图消除对一场看似失败的军事行动的指责</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 20:02:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-18/ty-article/.premium/cabinet-official-the-war-has-no-future-netanyahu-is-killing-time-to-evade-responsibility/0000018d-1ddc-db77-ad9f-dffe7d5a0000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫谋杀女游客嫌疑人被捕，在试图刺伤警察后被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-18/ty-article/.premium/suspect-in-murder-of-female-tourist-tel-aviv-arrested-shot-after-trying-to-stab-officers/0000018d-1d67-dd75-addd-ffe7d9980000</link><description>路人和邻居发现烟雾并致电消防部门后，这名 35 岁的游客被发现死在特拉维夫的一间公寓里。警方表示，现场调查结果表明，嫌疑人刺伤了该女子，然后放火烧毁了公寓</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 18:21:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-18/ty-article/.premium/suspect-in-murder-of-female-tourist-tel-aviv-arrested-shot-after-trying-to-stab-officers/0000018d-1d67-dd75-addd-ffe7d9980000</guid></item><item><title>东耶路撒冷居民可能因发表批评以色列的帖子而被剥夺公民身份</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-18/ty-article/.premium/east-jerusalem-resident-could-be-denied-citizenship-due-to-posts-critical-of-israel/0000018d-1cf9-db77-ad9f-dffb40820000</link><description>人口和移民局表示，鉴于社交媒体帖子“显示出明显的民族主义意识”，与效忠以色列不一致，正在考虑拒绝。申请人说，“我认为在民主国家，应该可以说出你的想法”</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 17:20:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-18/ty-article/.premium/east-jerusalem-resident-could-be-denied-citizenship-due-to-posts-critical-of-israel/0000018d-1cf9-db77-ad9f-dffb40820000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼MK因11年前担任警察期间涉嫌殴打被拘留者而受到讯问</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-18/ty-article/.premium/far-right-mk-questioned-on-suspicion-of-beating-detainees-while-on-duty-11-years-ago/0000018d-1c93-d022-ad9d-1eb7400c0000</link><description>据怀疑，极右翼 Otzma Yehudit 党的 MK Almog Cohen 与一群警察袭击了三名被拘留者。 2022 年，科恩发布了一张被拘留者双手被绑在地板上的照片，并将自己与该事件联系起来，此案重新审理。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 17:10:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-18/ty-article/.premium/far-right-mk-questioned-on-suspicion-of-beating-detainees-while-on-duty-11-years-ago/0000018d-1c93-d022-ad9d-1eb7400c0000</guid></item><item><title>中东的混乱并不全是加沙战争的溢出效应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-18/ty-article/.premium/the-chaos-in-the-middle-east-is-not-all-an-overspill-of-the-gaza-war/0000018d-1cd1-d022-ad9d-1ef5574a0000</link><description>尽管许多不同地方的冲突让美国显得毫无头绪和语无伦次，但拜登政府正在为该地区及其未来安全制定一个看似合理且令人信服的愿景</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 16:20:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-18/ty-article/.premium/the-chaos-in-the-middle-east-is-not-all-an-overspill-of-the-gaza-war/0000018d-1cd1-d022-ad9d-1ef5574a0000</guid></item><item><title>前部长、以色列宪法之父阿姆农·鲁宾斯坦 (Amnon Rubinstein) 去世，享年 92 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-18/ty-article/.premium/former-minister-father-of-israeli-constitutional-law-amnon-rubinstein-dies-at-92/0000018d-1d0c-dd75-addd-ffed8b390000</link><description>鲁宾斯坦曾担任伊扎克·拉宾政府的教育部长，也是《人类尊严和自由基本法》颁布背后的精神支柱</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 15:55:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-18/ty-article/.premium/former-minister-father-of-israeli-constitutional-law-amnon-rubinstein-dies-at-92/0000018d-1d0c-dd75-addd-ffed8b390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列没有阿拉伯社区有资格获得国家资助的枪支发放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-18/ty-article/.premium/only-jewish-communities-are-eligible-for-state-sponsored-gun-handout-arabs-are-left-out/0000018d-1be5-db77-ad9f-dff702560000</link><description>国家安全部拒绝公布符合资格的社区名单或所采用的标准，但查看该部网站发现：连边境的阿拉伯社区都没有被列入名单，而邻近的犹太社区，即使距离较远，也被列入名单。包括</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 15:50:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-18/ty-article/.premium/only-jewish-communities-are-eligible-for-state-sponsored-gun-handout-arabs-are-left-out/0000018d-1be5-db77-ad9f-dff702560000</guid></item><item><title>警方推翻将反战示威转移到偏远地区的决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-18/ty-article/.premium/police-reverse-decision-to-move-left-wing-demonstration-to-remote-location/0000018d-1cf3-d022-ad9d-1ef7a8070000</link><description>针对警方禁止在海法市举行反战抗议的决定向高等法院提起的上诉，以色列总检察长写道，该命令“不相称”，并强调抗议的权利“民主国家的基石，尤其是在紧急状态下”</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 15:42:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-18/ty-article/.premium/police-reverse-decision-to-move-left-wing-demonstration-to-remote-location/0000018d-1cf3-d022-ad9d-1ef7a8070000</guid></item></channel></rss>